My study of the album art of Emerson, Lake, and Palmer's "Tarkus" on a whiteboard with expo markers. Graphic artist William Neal created his magnum-opus of psychedelic art from a refinement of doodles of the armadillo-tank that came to be known as Tarkus. Later on in history Tarkus became a battlebot; this proved to be an unsuccessful venture- Tarkus lost every battle in the arena. That was the last the world saw of Tarkus, a tragic fall from grace for an armadillo battle tank that reached number 1 on the UK charts in 1971. #tarkus #battlebot #battlebots #emersonlakeandpalmer #williamneal #whiteboard #expomarker #whiteboardart #doodle #albumart #progrock #psychedelicrock #prog #manticore #pterodactyl #armadillo #armadillotank #art

Yo! Still here, still working away behind the scenes, and still checking in on Insta to see what you lovely folks are up to 🤓 I'm currently shaking up things in my own cleaning businesses, hence the lack of social 😱 I found a lot of the processes we had and have had for years, in my cleaning businesses didn't work as well as we've started to expand out of our local area, so it was back to the ol' drawing board and developing new processes that do work, no matter how far a branch may be from me physically 👍🏻😁
It's a lot of leg work, testing and tweaking but we're getting there and it has been good to go back to basics in some ways too 🤓 When was the last time you looked at how your business was working and if there are any cheaper/faster/better ways of doing the things you do? 🤔 You know one of the fastest ways to kill your business is to be in a 'we've always done it this way' mentality 🙈 Stagnation = death to a business ☠️ Back soon with new content, videos and some new fandangled softwares I've started using in my #residentialcleaning business that may help you guys too 🙌🏻 Back soon my loves but for right now, sorting my business takes priority 👊🏻😍 #busybee  #workingonmyshit #workingonmybusiness #businessdevelopment #fromthegroundup #backtobasics #quote #wordsofwisdom #buildanempire #solopreneur #fromabove #process #whiteboard #cleaningservice #cleaningservices #cleaningcompany #cleaningcrew #walkmytalk #workinghard #raisingmygame #workworkwork #focused #letsdothis 👊🏻😍👊🏻
